WEBVTT

00:11:28.880 --> 00:11:30.096
as I was doing --

00:11:30.120 --> 00:11:31.880
all totally wrong.

00:11:35.680 --> 00:11:38.880
So I got involved
in violent jihad in the mid '80s,

00:11:39.960 --> 00:11:41.440
starting with Afghanistan.

00:11:42.600 --> 00:11:45.880
And by the time I finished
it was in the year 2000.

00:11:47.040 --> 00:11:48.616
I was completely immersed in it.

00:11:48.640 --> 00:11:50.576
All around me people supported,

00:11:50.600 --> 00:11:51.816
applauded,

00:11:51.840 --> 00:11:54.240
even celebrated what
we were doing in their name.

00:11:56.160 --> 00:11:57.976
But by the time I learned to get out,

00:11:58.000 --> 00:12:00.616
completely disillusioned in the year 2000,